---
import { SITE_TITLE, CATEGORIES } from '../consts';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-32 border-t border-ink-600 bg-ink-950">
  <div class="container-x py-20">
    <!-- top: brand mark centered -->
    <div class="mb-16 text-center">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-baseline gap-3">
        <span class="font-display text-5xl leading-none tracking-tight text-ink-50">Lincoln</span>
        <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest-3 text-gold-500">Brief</span>
      </a>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-6 h-px w-16 bg-gold-500"></div>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-md text-sm text-ink-200">
        매일 아침, 미국·한국 증시의 핵심을 한 페이지로.<br/>
        시황 · 종목 · 예측 · 이슈.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <h3 class="eyebrow mb-5">Editions</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-100">
          {CATEGORIES.map((c) => (
            <li>
              <a href={`/category/${c.slug}/`} class="hover:text-gold-400">{c.name}</a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="eyebrow mb-5">House</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-100">
          <li><a href="/about/" class="hover:text-gold-400">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/" class="hover:text-gold-400">전체 글</a></li>
          <li><a href="/rss.xml" class="hover:text-gold-400">RSS</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="border-t border-ink-700">
    <div class="container-x flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-3 py-6 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest-2 text-ink-300 md:flex-row">
      <p class="font-mono">© {year} {SITE_TITLE.toUpperCase()}. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</p>
      <p class="text-center">본 콘텐츠는 투자 권유가 아니며, 모든 책임은 본인에게 있습니다.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
